data.description: This spacious 4-bedroom, 2-bath home offers a comfortable and convenient living experience. The property boasts a large utility room, providing ample storage and organization options. Additionally, a generously-sized bonus room offers versatile space for various activities. The fenced-in backyard ensures privacy and safety for outdoor enjoyment. Perfectly situated, this home is in close proximity to schools, making it ideal for families, as well as convenient for shopping, with retail outlets within easy reach. You'll find the local public library nearby for all your reading and learning needs, and churches are also in close proximity, offering a sense of community and convenience for religious activities. This property combines comfort, functionality, and a prime location for a well-rounded living experience.
